M162 P-2.304 Q.255 ; expect DRO 
M163 P0 Q00.10
M160 P34
M161 P25 Q25
M166 P0             ; no jump
M165 P1				; pitch

M00 ; nrcc?? yes , alloes EDM cut
;vvv
M198 ; will be replaced by a trap at end of state machibne
;^^^

M197

;  SEDM.restart should be FALSE ( if 2nd pass thru SM happened)

G0Z1 ; move tp a 3rf posn
G0X3Y0
